{"tid":1025034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本氣象主播撞樣台灣政壇美女　網民：加入AKB48都毫無違和感","createTime":"2019-02-17T04:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T06:51:25.000Z","uid":187437,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbb129142025d1d51eaf27e2727e66119c4f63a","tid":1025034,"uid":187437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"近來台灣政壇裡美女如雲，知名YouTuber蔡阿嘎去年甚至還特地拍了一部10大美女議員候選人的影片，而其中最有名的美女莫過於台北市議員高嘉瑜，即使已經快要40歲了，仍然保養得很好，看起來就好比鄰家大姊姊一般！而最近有網友在批踢踢表特板以「東京陳思宇」為題發了一篇文，發現日本有位美女主播，與先前投入北市立委選戰的陳思宇有點相像，掀起一陣討論，究竟她是何方神聖呢？讓我們趕緊看下去！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2415285/org/8deab93e8d030112729d21be230f8a71.jpg/iC-bjSagm8vdgYYWCQGhx6Nwh6KwlaD7_5Fhnf-RYZ0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2415285%2Forg%2F8deab93e8d030112729d21be230f8a71.jpg%2FiC-bjSagm8vdgYYWCQGhx6Nwh6KwlaD7_5Fhnf-RYZ0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7256bd8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n森山るり是日本東京電視台的氣象主播，長相甜美清新，氣質滿點，平常喜歡跳舞，也時常在Instagram上面和大家分享跳舞的影片，她的舞蹈活潑可愛、趣味十足，親民形象深植人心，廣受粉絲喜愛，現在IG上有高達4萬3千多人追蹤，魅力可見一般，就連本編我都抵擋不住她的魅力被圈粉了！<br />\n<br />\n仔細一看，森山るり好像真的與陳思宇有那麼一點相像，許多網友看完照片後紛紛推文表示：「蠻像的啊，皮膚比較好的版本」、「雖然思宇也不差，但我還是得說森山美多了」、「第一張很像啊，說真的陳思宇不賴啊」、「第一張真的超像XD」，看完大家的推文，結論大概是森山るり確實與陳思宇有點像，不過是進化升級後的版本XD不知道大家覺得呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2415295/org/cd4c838818fcf8e3757806f13d23472e.jpg/65u6h6IGVkaCxzfZwjrGdse_bSgwNLv0QMpp_UDKaf0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2415295%2Forg%2Fcd4c838818fcf8e3757806f13d23472e.jpg%2F65u6h6IGVkaCxzfZwjrGdse_bSgwNLv0QMpp_UDKaf0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e3441e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說這也不是森山るり第一次上表特板了，其實早在2017年9月和2018年4月就有上過啦～雖然OP了很多次，但每次都能吸引到不少推文，果然美女看不膩！而森山るり除了先前說的常在IG放上跳舞的影片，也常常分享自己的日常生活，從中還發現原來森山在2017年的時候曾經去到台灣玩！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2415300/org/e300edd68fe02e03cdcda6ad8a93f778.png/TwHL0q7-APgBUWCDSCXAhj5fVh2PAWmxW87PWFvOz1g?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2415300%2Forg%2Fe300edd68fe02e03cdcda6ad8a93f778.png%2FTwHL0q7-APgBUWCDSCXAhj5fVh2PAWmxW87PWFvOz1g%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=be3fddfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送給大家一張我很喜歡的照片，這躺在床上惹人憐愛的模樣，可愛的啦！會讓人很想要捏她臉頰一下呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2415309/org/01a5872e72d116a93e76264241ce63ae.png/5iHy3uC8PM_keIo1rA_2KuvSyYQn--XBUKTHflCkx34?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2415309%2Forg%2F01a5872e72d116a93e76264241ce63ae.png%2F5iHy3uC8PM_keIo1rA_2KuvSyYQn--XBUKTHflCkx34%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a9a7a336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/292645/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E6%92%9E%E6%A8%A3%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5akb48%E9%83%BD%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E9%81%95%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F292645%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A3%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5akb48%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%25AF%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2584%259F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=c4c53787\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/292645/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E6%92%9E%E6%A8%A3%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5akb48%E9%83%BD%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E9%81%95%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F</a>"},{"pid":"c89599befd083191c0c5f1a5a81cc5eca71590c9","tid":1025034,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-1